            "title": "For loop",
            "id": 127580,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Usando <strong>loops for</strong>, podemos escrever programas com muito menos código e torná-los mais fáceis de entender para outros programadores.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"_\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;**********---------&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"_\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;-------------------&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "For loop",
            "id": 127581,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para criar um loop <code>for</code> como este, adicionamos a palavra-chave <code>for</code>, uma variável como <code>i</code>, a palavra <code>in</code> e, finalmente, um intervalo <code>1...5</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"5\" /><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option startIndex=\"9\" endIndex=\"14\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>for</code> seguido de <code>i</code> e depois <code>in</code>, <code>1...5</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "For loop",
            "id": 127583,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
